## Responsive Design

### Breakpoint Strategy

| Breakpoint | Width Range | Circle Size | Velocity | Count |
|-----------|------------|-------------|----------|-------|
| Mobile | <640px | 20-60px | 0.3x | 10-15 |
| Tablet | 640-1023px | 40-100px | 0.5x | 15-25 |
| Desktop | ≥1024px | 60-160px | 0.7x | 20-40 |

### Dynamic Calculations

**Circle Count Formula:**
```typescript
const area = width * height;
const referenceArea = 1920 * 1080; // 1080p screen
const ratio = area / referenceArea;
const count = Math.floor(20 * ratio);
// Clamp between 10 and 40
```

**Size Calculation:**
```typescript
function getRandomSize(width: number): number {
  if (width < 640) return Math.random() * 40 + 20;
  if (width < 1024) return Math.random() * 60 + 40;
  return Math.random() * 100 + 60;
}
```

**Velocity Multiplier:**
```typescript
function getVelocityMultiplier(width: number): number {
  if (width < 640) return 0.3;
  if (width < 1024) return 0.5;
  return 0.7;
}
```

### Window Resize Handling

```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  const updateDimensions = () => {
    setDimensions({ width: window.innerWidth, height: window.innerHeight });
    regenerateCircles(); // Create new circles for new size
  };

  updateDimensions();
  window.addEventListener('resize', updateDimensions);
  return () => window.removeEventListener('resize', updateDimensions);
}, []);
```

